# Tutorial Videos Folder (20 Steps)

Place your tutorial video files here. Each video corresponds to a tutorial step.

## Home Page Steps (1-11)
- tutorial-welcome.mp4 (Step 1: Welcome/Project intro)
- tutorial-sidebar.mp4 (Step 2: Opening/closing sidebar)
- tutorial-nav.mp4 (Step 3: Navigating between sections)
- tutorial-camera.mp4 (Step 4: Switching camera views)
- tutorial-time.mp4 (Step 5: Changing time of day)
- tutorial-weather.mp4 (Step 6: Changing weather conditions)
- tutorial-rotate.mp4 (Step 7: Toggling auto-rotate)
- tutorial-reset.mp4 (Step 8: Resetting camera view)
- tutorial-language.mp4 (Step 9: Switching languages)
- tutorial-accessibility.mp4 (Step 10: Accessibility options)
- tutorial-help.mp4 (Step 11: Help/tutorial button)

## Units Page Steps (12-16)
- tutorial-sections.mp4 (Step 12: Building section tabs)
- tutorial-filters.mp4 (Step 13: Using unit filters)
- tutorial-available.mp4 (Step 14: Available only toggle)
- tutorial-unitcard.mp4 (Step 15: Interacting with unit cards)
- tutorial-compare.mp4 (Step 16: Comparing units)

## Surroundings Page Steps (17-20)
- tutorial-mapstyles.mp4 (Step 17: Changing map styles)
- tutorial-search.mp4 (Step 18: Searching for places)
- tutorial-categories.mp4 (Step 19: Filtering POI categories)
- tutorial-poibrowser.mp4 (Step 20: Browsing POI list)

## Recommended Specs
- Resolution: 320x180 or 640x360
- Duration: 3-8 seconds each
- Format: MP4 (H.264)
- Loop-friendly (end state similar to start)
